<p class="">The election of the Prime Minister was endorsed by the full sentiment of the whole country.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-6755d816-0612-442b-8ce0-cce759027b23" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
