<p class="">I should not have been so crude on that point.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-6126b342-3a80-4375-b9e0-5eb0f832bfce" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
