<p class="">I never said anything of the sort. I must make it absolutely clear that it does not rest with any Prime Minister to dissolve Parliament. The utmost he can do is to tender advice to the Crown.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
